## Required final validation

Run these commands and report results:

```bash
cd ~/zdash
APP_ENV=development \
DATABASE_URL=sqlite:///./zdash_test.db \
PRODUCTION_SAFETY_LOCK=true \
DRY_RUN=true \
LIVE_TRADING_ACK=false \
make validate-fast
```

Then, if Docker is available:

```bash
cd ~/zdash
APP_ENV=development \
DATABASE_URL=sqlite:///./zdash_test.db \
PRODUCTION_SAFETY_LOCK=true \
DRY_RUN=true \
LIVE_TRADING_ACK=false \
make validate
```

